data.description: PRICE REDUCTION WITH A MOTIVATED SELLER. Send your offers to this Beautiful home that features a fabulous POOL to relax and refresh every day, not to mention gatherings galore in a completely fenced in private backyard. It has many extras as well, including transferrable solar panels with great power savings, a Newer 2022 Roof, a Home recently painted inside out, brand new doors and closets throughout, a Newer 4-ton A/C 2020, Back windows double pane, a new sliding door in the master room. The Open kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances including an LG smart Refrigerator, a double oven stove, and a dishwasher included. The kitchen was remodeled in 2019, the Master bath remodel in 2022, as well as 2022 ceiling fans. Newer kitchen with solid wood cabinets. This is one you do not want to miss this time around.
